      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Order (BE truth → FE snapshot) · GetOrder enriches each item\nOrder { id, order_number, table_id, table_name, status, total_amount, items[] }\nOrderItem { id, product_id|combo_id, combo_ref_id, name, unit_price,\n            quantity, qty_served, note }\n★ ItemStatus is DERIVED itemStatus(qty_served,quantity) — NO status column\n★ combo header row: combo_id set, combo_ref_id=null, unit_price=0 (filtered from progress)",
