      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "frameId": null,
      "text": "• ItemStatus = itemStatus(qty_served,quantity): 0=pending · 0<n<qty=preparing · n=qty=done  (NO column)\n• RecalculateTotalAmount = SUM(unit_price × quantity) over remaining items  • Cancel order: SumQtyServedAndQuantity, reject if served/total ≥ 0.30",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• ItemStatus = itemStatus(qty_served,quantity): 0=pending · 0<n<qty=preparing · n=qty=done  (NO column)\n• RecalculateTotalAmount = SUM(unit_price × quantity) over remaining items  • Cancel order: SumQtyServedAndQuantity, reject if served/total ≥ 0.30",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
